<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Campos & Machado | Clínica Odontológica</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@500;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
--bege:#f5efe6;
--bordo:#6b1f2b;
--azul:#1f3a5f;
--preto:#111111;
--cinza:#555555;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;background:var(--bege);color:var(--preto);}
header{background:var(--preto);color:white;padding:60px 20px;text-align:center;}
header h1{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:44px;letter-spacing:1px;}
header p{margin-top:10px;color:#ddd;}
section{padding:100px 10%;opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px);transition:all 0.8s ease;}
section.visible{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}
.premium{background:white;border-radius:24px;padding:70px;box-shadow:0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);}
.premium h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:34px;margin-bottom:30px;color:var(--bordo);}
.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:60px;align-items:center;}
.profile-img{width:100%;max-width:420px;border-radius:24px;box-shadow:0 25px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);}
.button{display:inline-block;padding:16px 32px;background:var(--bordo);color:white;text-decoration:none;border-radius:40px;margin-top:25px;font-weight:500;transition:0.3s;}
.button:hover{background:var(--azul);} 
.treatments ul{list-style:none;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px;}
.treatments li{background:var(--bege);padding:20px;border-radius:16px;border-left:5px solid var(--bordo);font-weight:500;color:var(--cinza);}
footer{text-align:center;padding:50px 20px;background:var(--preto);color:white;}
.whatsapp-float{position:fixed;bottom:25px;right:25px;background:#25D366;border-radius:50%;width:65px;height:65px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);z-index:1000;}
.whatsapp-float svg{width:32px;height:32px;fill:white;}
iframe{border-radius:20px;width:100%;height:350px;border:none;margin-top:30px;}
@media(max-width:900px){.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;text-align:center;} .treatments ul{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
<h1>Campos & Machado</h1>
<p>Clínica Odontológica Premium | Campinas - SP</p>
</header>

<section>
<div class="premium">
<h2>Cirurgião-Dentista</h2>
<div class="grid">
<div>
<p>Atendimento personalizado com excelência técnica e abordagem humanizada. Estrutura moderna, conforto e alto padrão em cada detalhe.</p>
<p style="margin-top:15px;"><strong>Dr. Victor Campos</strong><br>Cirurgião-Dentista<br>CRO: 159354</p>
<a class="button" href="https://wa.me/5519999999999" target="_blank">Agendar Consulta</a>
</div>
<div>
<img src="dr-victor.jpg" alt="Dr. Victor Campos" class="profile-img">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<section>
<div class="premium treatments">
<h2>Tratamentos</h2>
<ul>
<li>Limpeza</li>
<li>Cirurgia Oral</li>
<li>Implantes</li>
<li>Urgências Odontológicas</li>
<li>Atendimento 24 horas</li>
<li>Prótese Dentária</li>
<li>Reabilitação Oral</li>
<li>Lentes de Contato Dental</li>
</ul>
</div>
</section>

<section>
<div class="premium">
<h2>Localização</h2>
<p>Rua Frei Manoel da Ressurreição Nº 916<br>2º andar sala 03<br>Campinas - SP</p>
<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=Rua+Frei+Manoel+da+Ressurreição+916+Campinas&output=embed"></iframe>
</div>
</section>

<footer>
<p>© 2026 Campos & Machado - Clínica Odontológica Premium</p>
</footer>

<a href="https://wa.me/5519999999999" class="whatsapp-float" target="_blank" aria-label="WhatsApp">
<svg viewBox="0 0 32 32">
<path d="M16 .4C7.4.4.4 7.3.4 16c0 2.8.7 5.5 2.1 7.9L0 32l8.3-2.2c2.3 1.3 4.9 2 7.7 2 8.6 0 15.6-6.9 15.6-15.6S24.6.4 16 .4zm0 28.7c-2.4 0-4.8-.7-6.8-1.9l-.5-.3-4.9 1.3 1.3-4.8-.3-.5C3.6 20.9 3 18.5 3 16 3 8.8 8.8 3 16 3s13 5.8 13 13-5.8 13-13 13zm7.2-9.8c-.4-.2-2.3-1.1-2.7-1.2-.4-.2-.6-.2-.9.2-.3.4-1 1.2-1.2 1.4-.2.2-.5.3-.9.1-.4-.2-1.6-.6-3-1.8-1.1-1-1.8-2.2-2-2.6-.2-.4 0-.6.2-.8.2-.2.4-.5.6-.7.2-.2.3-.4.4-.6.1-.2 0-.5 0-.7 0-.2-.9-2.2-1.2-3-.3-.8-.6-.7-.9-.7h-.8c-.3 0-.7.1-1 .5-.3.4-1.3 1.3-1.3 3.1 0 1.8 1.3 3.5 1.5 3.7.2.2 2.5 3.8 6.1 5.3.9.4 1.6.6 2.2.8.9.3 1.7.3 2.4.2.7-.1 2.3-.9 2.6-1.8.3-.9.3-1.6.2-1.8-.1-.2-.3-.3-.7-.5z"/>
